    Class Description
    Chest

    This represents an enemy that hurts the character on contact.
    Obstacle
    This class represents an obstacle that prevents the character from moving past.
    RiddleBank
    This class represents the riddle bank where riddles are drawn from.
    Sprite
    This class represents a default sprite.
    Turtle
    This class represents the main character which is controlled by the player using arrowkeys.
